    "description": "The Broadmore family of products offer a unique economical means of provisioning, grooming, and routing TDM DS3, DS1, E3, E1 services and mixed-speed serial data to logical ATM connections. The Broadmore/SSHield Management Module controls the Broadmore configuration parameters using SSHield, an implementation of the IETF SECSH protocol, which provides an authenticated, encrypted data communications channel for secure management. More information can also be found on www.teamf1.com and www.carrieraccess.com.",
